to the graphical user interface that millions of worldwide users are
accustomed to, resembling a mixture of the Apple Macintosh environment
and IBM's OS/2 system.
It is currently being beta-tested all over the world by thousands of
developers who have made the new system a part of their business
schedules but users tend to adopt new operating systems over a period of
a few years.
