> MICROSOFT DELAYS CHICAGO O/S
------------------------------
"Forget about seeing Chicago under your Christmas tree this year.
Officials at Microsoft Corp. concede that the eagerly awaited upgrade to
Windows and DOS may not reach users before the Cubs begin spring
training in 1995.
